dcterms:description: The CIFAR-10 dataset is utilized for both model training and validation, comprising 60,000 entries with dimensions of 32x32 pixels. The dataset is employed in three distinct configurations: Full Dataset, Partial Dataset, and Imbalanced Dataset, to evaluate the performance of the proposed Damage GAN model.
dcterms:title: CIFAR-10
